{"tid":1295031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊：修例爭議後特首或想辭職　兩問責官員換人不難","createTime":"2019-07-08T01:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:56:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c76ac41e7b4b4898c4b6152ca0e5a3a6fddec739","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，在反對修訂《逃犯條例》事件後，感覺行政長官林鄭月娥想辭職，因為再做下去只會日日被人指責，民望評分比前特首梁振英還低，以前做任何事都是第一，現時在市民心中「排第尾」，相信對她的打擊很大，但估計林鄭月娥要繼續「頂下去」完成手尾，都是正確。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司司長鄭若驊及保安局局長李家超的去留，田北俊出席一個電台節目時說，相信要填補兩人的空缺並不難，例如可由即將退休的警務處處長盧偉聰接任保安局局長。<br />\n<br />\n不過田北俊提到，司長局是由中央任命，反而行政會議成員是由特首任命，建議可重組行會，田北俊建議黨主席張宇人辭去行會成員之外，點名另外兩名行會成員辭職，包括本身是資深大律師的湯家驊及新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首，而葉劉淑儀就極力支持修例。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fb7b03ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5b2da995\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fc7bea15f41e81ab4dfde7eb8fdd75a54b61d7a5","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警務處處長盧偉聰接任保安局局長</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好喇掛"},{"pid":"6d2673e227941a5874d125796c9808853fcb8f50","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n不過田北俊提到，司長局是由中央任命，反而行政會議成員是由特首任命，建議可重組行會，田北俊建議黨主席張宇人辭去行會成員之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">點名另外兩名行會成員辭職，包括本身是資深大律師的湯家驊及新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首，而葉劉淑儀就極力支持修例。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fb7b03ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5b2da995\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4aed69168c2d72cf31fb29b3b6ba05a8522ff1f","tid":1295031,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2673e227941a5874d125796c9808853fcb8f50","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n不過田北俊提到，司長局是由中央任命，反而行政會議成員是由特首任命，建議可重組行會，田北俊建議黨主席張宇人辭去行會成員之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">點名另外兩名行會成員辭職，包括本身是資深大律師的湯家驊及新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首，而葉劉淑儀就極力支持修例。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fb7b03ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5b2da995\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"辭職準備參選下屆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157ed6cb544e05802f74086b1195c1ff9b1b9be9","tid":1295031,"uid":52200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:00:50.000Z","msg":"場仗未打完架！五大訴求未接納，一眾被捕士未釋放，林鄭未鞠躬，盧偉聰未落台，外國戰線啱啱先開始(在此向攬炒巴致敬)，現階邊個同政府對話邊個就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEbbGfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEbbGfV.jpg&h=252d433f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMfoug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMfoug.jpg&h=5527c394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANusVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANusVW.jpg&h=5737c822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QQzD2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QQzD2C.jpg&h=5961c3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0zD2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0zD2D.jpg&h=747e3cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0LLHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0LLHD.jpg&h=496d3a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZythBPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZythBPj.jpg&h=f98e34dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f3a1e795ae87497541895279e9d477929c496b","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f01ab3aa280103ef149e0f6b6758958252f4cab","tid":1295031,"uid":67294,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"fc7bea15f41e81ab4dfde7eb8fdd75a54b61d7a5","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警務處處長盧偉聰接任保安局局長</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好喇掛"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"都唔係, 李家超份人直情係︰你咪屌囉, 吹得我漲咩 咁既態度<br />\n但盧偉聰開記招至少會怯同埋道歉, 起碼似返個人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就奇啦, 全部下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994ff85ae65cdb9cd90f9ba87ab66a0cba70d60e","tid":1295031,"uid":33668,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:05:25.000Z","msg":"田北俊基本上代表哂大陸同香港商人嘅睇法<br />\n仲挾大灣經濟以令豬頭<br />\n佢G2000 比大陸告應該都深明逃犯有幾幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14c9c8a2281ceb027b61cb0a5c3820e0a709578","tid":1295031,"uid":147367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"on9，盧偉聰犯左錯仲有得升職"},{"pid":"30c0f14eac72a3bc487507edd726cb9a6352efc0","tid":1295031,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"自由黨4名榮譽主席將去信張宇人促辭任行會成員<br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，政府在修訂《逃犯條例》工作上做得不足，既然官員不下台，行政會議應該重組，<span style=\"color: red;\">自由黨4名榮譽主席將去信黨主席張宇人，建議他辭去行政會議員成員一職</span>。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊出席一個電台節目時說，在上月9日百萬人上街反對修例後，自由黨隨即出聲明，表態支持政府如期恢復二讀，田北俊透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">黨魁鍾國斌表明反對，但主席張宇人連同另外兩名立法會議員易志明及邵家輝就支持</span>，最終發出有關聲明，田北俊認為做法是犯了錯誤，等同「幫兇」，做法太過倉卒。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊認為，作為行會成員，應代表黨到行政會議反映市民意見，而並非行會成員綑綁政黨。他說，如果張宇人拒絕辭去行會成員，他要視乎<span style=\"color: red;\">下一步行動，包括黨友意見，但承認或會出現退黨潮</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467154-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht